\id 3JN - Maya-Tektiteko NT -Guatemala 2003 (DBL -2013) 
\h Toxi' U'j Stz'ib'en Wa'nch 
\toc1 Te Toxi' U'j Stz'ib'en Wa'nch 
\toc2 Toxi' U'j Stz'ib'en Wa'nch 
\toc3 3Wnch 
\mt1 Te Toxi' U'j Stz'ib'en Wa'nch 
\c 1  
\s1 Jun Limb'il 
\p  
\v 1 Wetz aj tijxjal a'in [aj at wajwalil kxol kye qerman], wetz nqet ntz'ib'a' ja u'jni te yatz wamiw Gay\x * \xo 1:1 \xt Kya 19:29; Rom 16:23; 1Kor 1:14\x* aj b'an b'an'ax ajb'ila' a'ich witza'.  
\v 2 Yatz erman aj b'an ganimich, wetz nkyinxnaq'tzan tuky'i Qtata Dios tzan tel galan kyaqil awuky'i'l iktza'x te galan n'ok tuj awanim, b'ix tzaj tsi'xwit jun axwinqlal.  
\v 3 Wetz nim nkyinchalaj tuq aj kyul txq'an qerman b'ix otzaj kyq'uma' kyaqil titza' yatz nchb'et, qa yatz k'onti'l nkaj asi' tzan ab'et tuj te tume'l b'an'ax.\x * \xo 1:3 \xt 2Wnch 4\x* 
\v 4 Wetz k'onti'l junky tidi' aj mas nkyinchalaj ti'j sinoke oj tok ncha'o' qa kye nk'wa'al\f + \fr 1:4 \ft “K'wa'al” tuj ja taqanni telponx kye aj oxik nxnaq'tza' te tpakb'alil ti'j te Qajaw Jesus kyetz.\f* nkyeb'et tuj te b'an'ax. 
\s1 Qo'onen Kyuky'i Kye Qerman Laq'chik Xjal Aj Nkye'ul Pakb'on Qxol 
\p  
\v 5 Yatz erman aj ganimich, galan nchk'ulun tzan k'on kaj asi' tzan awonen kxol kye qerman b'ix mas kyuky'i kye aj [laq'chik xjal aj nkyepon exol b'ix] nya'tx otzqi'mj-e'.  
\v 6 Kyetz oje xik kyq'uma' kywitz kkyaqil kye qerman titza' yatz nkyeqet agani'. Galan qa yatz nlay kaj asi' tzan awonen kyuky'i'l tuky'i te aj presis te kyetz, iktza' te Qtata Dios tgan, b'ix ikxji b'a'n tzan kxik galan tuj kyb'ey.  
\v 7 Komo kyetz e'ex [tuj kyamaq' tzan kypakb'an] tzan tpaj nqet kygani' [te Qajawil], b'ix k'onti'l ma'tx ktzoqpij tzan kyok one' tzan kye aj k'onti'l nkye'okslan.  
\v 8 Astilji a'o' qetz presis tzan jk'amon kye qerman aj iktza' kyetz, tzan qonen kyuky'i'l tzan kypakb'an te b'an'ax. 
\s1 K'onti'l Tzan Tel Qin Kyi'j Txq'anky Te Aj Nya'tx Galan Nkyk'ulu' 
\p  
\v 9 Wetz oje xik nsama' jun u'j kye kyaqil qerman tzi, per te Diótrefes aj mer tgan tzan tok tetz tb'ay kxol kye qerman, tetz k'onti'l nqoqet toksla'.  
\v 10 Astilji qa okyinpoyon wetz tzi, okyinyoliyon kyuky'i kye qerman titza' tetz tidi'chq yol njaw b'antik titza', tidi'chq njaw tnik'o' qi'ja. B'ix pyor twitz nini, tetz k'onti'l nkyeqet tk'amo' kye qerman aj nkyepon, b'ix kye qerman tzi aj kygan tzan kyqet kyk'amo', tetz k'onti'l nstzoqpi' tzan kyk'ulun ikxji, qa kyetz nkyek'ulun ikxji ntons nkye'ex tlajo' kxol. 
\p  
\v 11 Yatz erman aj ganimich, k'on tz'el awin yatz aj nya'tx galan nqet yek'u' awitz, sinoke a'ox aj galan. Ab'l aj nk'ulun tume'l, te nini nb'et tuky'i Qtata Dios; yatzun te aj nk'ulun nya'tx galan, te nini k'onti'l totzqi' Qtata Dios.\x * \xo 1:11 \xt 1Wnch 2:29; 3:6-10\x* 
\v 12 Kyaqil nkyeyolin galan ti'j te Met, b'ix tetz nk'ulun ikxtza'x te Tyol Qtata Dios nyolin. Ax qetza ax nqoyolin galan ti'j tetz, b'ix yatz aweb'en tume'l nqoyolin. 
\s1 Jun Kawb'il 
\p  
\v 13 Wetz at tidi'chq tzan txik nq'uma' yatz per k'on ngan tzan txik nq'uma' cha tuj u'j  
\v 14 tzan tpaj lo'ik nk'u'j nlay kyinnachq'in tzan npon e'el yatz b'ix ngan yolin nwitzale' awuky'i'l.\x * \xo 1:14 \xt 2Wnch 12\x* 
\v 15 Qet chewsa'xwit ak'u'j. Kye tal awanab' nkyesaman jun limb'il te yatz.